{
  "description": "<p>Haul gear, pack extra clothing layers, food, water, and other supplies on long approaches. 1680-denier ballistic polyester stands up to being dragged around at the base of a route. The padded shoulder straps and hipbelt support the weight of your cargo and the panel-opening keeps the contents organized.</p><ul><li>Burly 1680-denier ballistic polyester with a PFC-free DWR finish and a PU coating for great water resistance</li><li>EVA foam padded shoulder straps, hipbelt and backpanel provide comfort</li><li>Shoulder straps have stretch woven fabric on the underside for comfort, and load lifter straps for fine tuned adjustments</li><li>Sternum strap is height adjustable</li><li>Access the cavernous main compartment through the top zipper or through the large zippered panel on the front of the pack</li><li>Tuck away rope strap stows away in its own compartment or can be deployed to keep your cord organized and at the ready</li><li>Flexpansion Pocket with roll top collar adds an additional 10L of space</li><li>Side pocket for quick access on the go</li><li>Buckled compression straps reduce pack volume</li><li>Webbing grab handle on top</li><li>Hydration compatible with hydration hanger loop inside bag</li></ul>",
